{"tid":2190944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12港人偷渡台灣失敗被捕！律師透露：恐遭中共判終身監禁","createTime":"2020-09-06T05:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T10:03:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b8a6127eb2ee8c4bdc38d7f6b169e15b1dd15cc","tid":2190944,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T05:52:26.000Z","msg":"中國海警上個月26日通報，廣東海警局在粵港東南方向管轄海域內查獲涉嫌非法越境的快艇1艘，抓獲李姓、鄧姓等12餘名港籍涉嫌非法越境人員，根據外媒報導，這些人是試圖潛逃台灣的的反送中人士；而其中一名被捕者家屬所委託的中國律師則透露，要前往看守所探視當事人時，遭到中國公安不少的阻撓與干涉，公安還表示這些港人可能不會被當成一般的偷渡客看待，而會被當局視為「組織偷渡」的人蛇集團主謀，最重將判處「終身監禁」！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=809749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D809749&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=f11cb9cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D809749&h=20f8a0a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=809749</a>"},{"pid":"04deafec9906581118756d6e2765f1820919ccfb","tid":2190944,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"救人！十二位手足有機會改控囚終身<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2190114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2190114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e69263f93e0526f4de0a1de13cc155632deda4cf","tid":2190944,"uid":62162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04deafec9906581118756d6e2765f1820919ccfb","tid":2190944,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T06:10:42.000Z","msg":"救人！十二位手足有機會改控囚終身<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2190114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2190114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:03:34.000Z","msg":"唔明點解會有人負評你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}